{"tid":1713772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大一戰絕對係勇武派抗爭標準","createTime":"2019-11-12T19:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:35:56.000Z","uid":66390,"like":134,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac3853d359359f2b89a6b37f2e3e05f3ccd4640","tid":1713772,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:42:37.000Z","msg":"分工有序！勇武抗爭！敢於創新！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>分工有序</ins></strong><br />\n兩條人鏈 分開兩排 齊齊整整<br />\n有後援溝酒<br />\n魔法一箱一箱咁運上前線<br />\n你係從來未聽過人鏈會叫「魔法！XX油！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>勇武抗爭</ins></strong><br />\n幾耐無見過齊整盾陣？你幾時？我印象中就721上環！<br />\n一路推推推 係咁掟魔法！掟到狗走！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>敢於創新</ins></strong><br />\n新類型工程車<br />\n開中大巴<br />\n因應地形 電單車係咁入 多到以為food panda停車場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">本身望住呢場運動頹頹地咁 但過左今日 又好似返返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">可能大家知道 <strong><em>我一定要守住呢到！</em></strong> 而你唔會好強烈覺得 「我要守住黃埔 銅鑼灣」 咁樣。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">總之真係好正 唔單只頹完返返來咁 而好似再進步左咁 </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry 我中左彈提早退場<br />\n我知出面仲打緊 <br />\n各位手足加油 小心 留命"},{"pid":"9be56b675a06ce52fabf4a3e15d43838a9bd5084","tid":1713772,"uid":66390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:44:35.000Z","msg":"但傷左好多個<br />\n一路入 一路有手足抬出來<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ad597a4c88d20a89ae82526aad308d7f89dd91","tid":1713772,"uid":66390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:45:34.000Z","msg":"大家應該每次都當某個地方<br />\n係自己要守既地方<br />\n信念強烈 行事先有勁"},{"pid":"c381134bdaa19042f268ef2103e57619d2ebb4c3","tid":1713772,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:46:04.000Z","msg":"手足辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481a8f12e5d2c16accc64419e2f2b88128a2c8c2","tid":1713772,"uid":66390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:46:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">要香港獨立</span><br />\n其中一個做法係： 先劃一個地方為佔領區 要守住佔領區 再宣布區內獨立/香港獨立 再慢慢擴大"},{"pid":"27e4838e57ac35aa4405bb74b74e9ce4bb4fcd78","tid":1713772,"uid":54326,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:47:48.000Z","msg":"大學生有知識係唔同啲火箭炮都整得出 你地今日真係好勁<br />\n啲毅進仔見到啲火用個盾撞開自己人 柒撚到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d7b3b9b6b20e67a0dd977a3106c1fba480025","tid":1713772,"uid":129990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:51:29.000Z","msg":"今日中大先至係真勇武"},{"pid":"c27b99f7ec6958f4c03daccb4be5c7f18f7b56b6","tid":1713772,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:51:56.000Z","msg":"火焰箭！"},{"pid":"d6f7390bd1b3b225f5331863d5c328dc00ae2472","tid":1713772,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:58:22.000Z","msg":"直情係香港之光"},{"pid":"d328923cccc9400d26052702043ec7ca4e28f3e8","tid":1713772,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"好多謝你地，重新燃起香港人希望之火！"},{"pid":"39a4e95d1aed514b7b0779d9c253c7a547b4364a","tid":1713772,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:03:59.000Z","msg":"中大之戰一定要寫入歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8a6db97a2f430b37dc70111ed721819e7fd170","tid":1713772,"uid":6221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:43:54.000Z","msg":"仲有最強和理非做後勤<img